Read in data

Show code 
db = read_excel(path="/Users/Andrew/Desktop/Chemomob/Dataset/Dataset 1.17.24.xlsx")

db <- db %>%
  filter(Two.txp == 0 & Mobilization != "Cy/Dex" & Mobilization != "Cy/Etop/pred") %>%
  filter(Study.num != 330 & Study.num !=  230 & Study.num !=  56 & Study.num !=  40 & Study.num != 22) %>% # 330 = G+P failure, 230 = pre-ASCT KRD-PACE debulking with prior non-CM mobilization, 56 = POEMS, 40 = POEMS, 22 = pre-ASCT KRD-PACE with prior non-CM mobilization
  #filter(Induction.lines >1 | Chemo.mob ==1) %>%
  mutate(
    Total.LPAM = as.factor(Total.LPAM),
    CMV.status = as.factor(CMV.status),
    Pre.mob.response = factor(Pre.mob.response, levels = c("CR","VGPR","PR","PD") ),
    Maintenance = factor(Maintenance, levels = c("Standard","None","High")),
    Cytogenetic.risk = factor(Cytogenetic.risk, levels = c("Standard","High")),
    #Chemo.mob = as.factor(Chemo.mob),
    Received.cefepime = as.numeric(Received.cefepime),
    Received.Vanco = as.numeric(Received.Vanco),
    Dx.date = ymd(Dx.date),
    txdate = ymd(txdate),
    Late.txp = ifelse(txdate - Dx.date >= 365,1,0),
    Time.to.tx = txdate - Dx.date,
    Real.death.or.DLC.date = ymd(Real.death.or.DLC.date),
    Progression.next.death.DLC.date = ymd(Progression.next.death.DLC.date),
    Real.days.DLC = Real.death.or.DLC.date - txdate,
    Real.days.progression.death.DLC = Progression.next.death.DLC.date - txdate,
    BL.M.spike = as.numeric(BL.M.spike),
    Pre.CM.M.spike = as.numeric(Pre.CM.M.spike),
    Post.CM.M.spike = as.numeric(Post.CM.M.spike),
    
    BL.kappa = as.numeric(BL.kappa),
    BL.lambda = as.numeric(BL.lambda),
    Pre.CM.kappa = as.numeric(Pre.CM.kappa),
    Pre.CM.lambda = as.numeric(Pre.CM.lambda),
    Post.CM.kappa = as.numeric(Post.CM.kappa),
    Post.CM.lambda = as.numeric(Post.CM.lambda),
    HRCA.num = recode(HRCAs, "0" = "0", "1" = "1", "2" = "2+", "3" = "2+"),
    Tx.year = year(txdate)
  )

CHANGES OVER TIME

Number of ASCTs over time

Show code 
db %>%
  filter(Tx.year >=2019 & Tx.year <2023) %>%
  count(Tx.year) %>%
  ggplot + aes(Tx.year, n) + 
  geom_point(stat="identity") + 
  geom_line(stat="identity", color="blue") + 
  ylab("Number of ASCTs") + 
  xlab(NULL) +
  geom_text(aes(label=n), position=position_stack(vjust=1.05)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel1") + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c( 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022)) +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16), axis.text = element_text(size = 16), legend.title = element_text(size = 16),legend.text = element_text(size = 14), axis.text.x=element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))

Bar graph of inpatient vs outpatient ASCTs

Show code 
## Counts
db %>%
  filter(Tx.year >=2019 & Tx.year <2023) %>%
  count(Pre.admit, Tx.year) %>%
  group_by(Tx.year) %>%
  mutate(
    pct = prop.table(n) * 100,
    Setting = factor(ifelse(Pre.admit==1,"Elective admission","Outpatient"), levels = c("Outpatient","Elective admission"))
    ) %>%
  ggplot + aes(Tx.year, n, fill = Setting) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  ylab("Number of patients") + 
  xlab(NULL) +
  geom_text(aes(label=paste0(n,sprintf("\n(%1.1f", pct),"%)")), position=position_stack(vjust=0.5)) + 
  #ggtitle("Infused over time") + 
  theme_classic() + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel1") + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022, 2023)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = c(20, 40, 60, 80, 100)) +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16), axis.text = element_text(size = 16), legend.title = element_text(size = 16),legend.text = element_text(size = 14), axis.text.x=element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))

db %>%
  filter(Tx.year >=2019 & Tx.year <2023) %>%
  count(Pre.admit, Tx.year) %>%
  group_by(Tx.year) %>%
  mutate(
    pct = prop.table(n) * 100,
    Setting = factor(ifelse(Pre.admit==1,"Elective admission","Outpatient"), levels = c("Outpatient","Elective admission"))
    ) %>%
  ggplot + aes(Tx.year, pct, fill = Setting) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  ylab("Proportion of patients (%)") + 
  xlab(NULL) +
  geom_text(aes(label=paste0(n,sprintf("\n(%1.1f", pct),"%)")), position=position_stack(vjust=0.5)) + 
  #ggtitle("Infused over time") + 
  theme_classic() + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel1") + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022, 2023)) +

Bar graph of ages

Show code 
## Counts
db %>%
  mutate(
    Age.category = case_when(
      txage <50 ~ "<50",
      txage >=50 & txage <55 ~ "50-55",
      txage >=55 & txage <60 ~ "55-60",
      txage >=60 & txage <65 ~ "60-65",
      txage >=65 ~ "\u226565",
      .default = "other"
    )
  ) %>%
  filter(Tx.year >=2019 & Tx.year <2023) %>%
  count(Age.category, Tx.year) %>%
  group_by(Tx.year) %>%
  mutate(
    pct = prop.table(n) * 100,
    Age = factor(Age.category, levels = c("<50", "50-55","55-60","60-65","\u226565") )
    ) %>%
  ggplot + aes(Tx.year, n, fill = Age) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  ylab("Number of patients") + 
  xlab(NULL) +
  geom_text(aes(label=paste0(n,sprintf(" (%1.1f", pct),"%)")), position=position_stack(vjust=0.5)) + 
  #ggtitle("Infused over time") + 
  theme_classic() + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel1") + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022, 2023)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = c(20,40,60,80,100)) +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16), axis.text = element_text(size = 16), legend.title = element_text(size = 16),legend.text = element_text(size = 14), axis.text.x=element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))

Bar graph of sex

## Counts
db %>%
  filter(Tx.year >=2019 & Tx.year <2023) %>%
  count(sex, Tx.year) %>%
  group_by(Tx.year) %>%
  mutate(
    pct = prop.table(n) * 100,
    Age = sex
    ) %>%
  ggplot + aes(Tx.year, n, fill = sex) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  ylab("Number of patients") + 
  xlab(NULL) +
  geom_text(aes(label=paste0(n,sprintf(" (%1.1f", pct),"%)")), position=position_stack(vjust=0.5)) + 
  #ggtitle("Infused over time") +
